Package com.foreach.across.modules.entity.views.processors.query

Class EQLStringValueOptionEnhancer<T>

java.lang.Object
com.foreach.across.modules.entity.views.processors.query.EntityQueryValueEnhancer<T>
com.foreach.across.modules.entity.views.processors.query.EQLStringValueOptionEnhancer<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Consumer<OptionFormElementBuilder>
public final class EQLStringValueOptionEnhancer<T> extends EntityQueryValueEnhancer<T>
Convert the raw value of an OptionFormElementBuilder to a String and returns it as a valid EQL string: surrounded with single quotes and pre-existing single quotes escaped.

Optionally provide a Function to apply to the raw value first. In that case the result of the function will be converted to the EQL string.

Since:
3.1.0
Author:
Arne Vandamme
